Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://github.com/benjamimgois/serialcom

Package: serialcom
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyqt6, picocom, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modern graphical interface for serial communication
 SerialCom is a modern and elegant graphical interface for serial
 communication via picocom. It provides an easy-to-use interface for
 configuring serial port parameters and establishing connections.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic serial port detection
  - Support for serial ports and USB adapters
  - Complete serial parameter configuration
  - Modern PyQt6 interface
